OL,3,CVehicle collides through front of
OL,4,CButterworths Solicitors in Penrith
OL,6,FA vehicle has collided through the
OL,7,Ffront of Butterworths Solicitors in
OL,8,FPenrith causing damage to the premises.
OL,10,FCumbria Police confirmed that they
OL,11,Freceived a report at 10:22am on
OL,12,FTuesday 24 February of a vehicle
OL,13,Fcolliding with the business at
OL,14,FCornmarket in the town.
OL,16,FIn a statement Cumbria Police said:
OL,17,F"Report came in at 10:22am ` reporting
OL,18,Fan RTC with one vehicle where it has
OL,19,Fcollided with the front of a business
OL,20,Fat the Cornmarket in Penrith, damage
OL,21,Fcaused to the building.
