OL,3,CVehicle collides through front of
OL,4,CButterworths Solicitors in Penrith
OL,6,F"No injuries caused to the driver."
OL,8,FButterworths Solicitors were one of
OL,9,Fthe legal brands of PM Law Group who
OL,10,Fare currently under investigation by
OL,11,Fthe Solicitors Regulation Authority
OL,12,F(SRA) into potential fraud.
OL,14,FThe firm shut suddenly on Monday 2
OL,15,FFebruary which has led to the SRA
OL,16,Finvestigation.
